.SH BUGS
The algorithm returns a 15 bit quantity on the PDP11; a 31 bit quantity
on the VAX.
.I Irand
on the PDP11 calls
.IR rand (3C)
twice to form a 31 bit quantity, but bit 15 will always be 0.
